description: Objets d’Égypte program, directed by Sylvie Denoix, which ran from 2008 until 2011. While the bibliographical databases are primarily focused on Egypt, they will in some cases cover a more extended area, including the Mediterranean, and/or the region of the Middle East and Africa. A bibliographical database concerning Byzantine and Islamic glass, authored by Maria Mossakowska-Gaubert, carried out as a part of the same program, is available on line since 2008 at http://www.ifao.egnet.net/bases/verre/

is_part_of.title: Bois travaillé du Ier au XVe sc. - 1st to 15th century worked wood
